    <li><strong>Guest channels</strong> — WhatsApp, SMS, email, web chat</li>
    <li><strong>Staff interfaces</strong> — Dashboard, internal messaging</li>
    <li><strong>Hotel systems</strong> — PMS, POS, housekeeping, maintenance</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    The AI chatbot handles routine guest requests automatically while intelligently routing complex issues to the right staff members with full context.
  </p>

