  <h2 id="who-is-it-for">Who is it for?</h2>

  <p>Jack is designed for hospitality businesses of all sizes:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Hotels</strong> — Boutique to mid-size properties</li>
    <li><strong>Vacation Rentals</strong> — Airbnb, VRBO, and direct bookings</li>
    <li><strong>Hostels</strong> — Budget-friendly accommodation</li>
    <li><strong>Property Managers</strong> — Managing multiple properties</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    If you're looking for an AI concierge without expensive monthly SaaS fees or giving guest data to third parties, Jack is for you.
  </p>

  <h2 id="how-it-works">How it works</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Guest sends a message</strong> — Via WhatsApp, SMS, email, or web chat
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Jack understands the request</strong> — Using AI to classify intent and extract details
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Jack responds or escalates</strong> — Answers automatically or routes to the right staff member
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Staff reviews if needed</strong> — Complex requests appear in the dashboard for human handling
    </li>
  </ol>

