  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>

  <p>
    Jack is <strong>free and open source</strong>. Your only costs are:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Hosting</strong> — Free tier on Railway/Render, or ~$5-10/month for production</li>
    <li><strong>AI API</strong> — ~$5-20/month for Claude/OpenAI, or $0 with local AI</li>
    <li><strong>Channels</strong> — WhatsApp Business API (Meta), Twilio for SMS (pay-as-you-go)</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    For a small property, expect <strong>under $20/month</strong> total. Compare that to $200-2000/month for commercial hotel chatbot solutions.
  </p>

